mapproperties.key: Waking up: -She was like on vacation. She did not care about the schedule, she did not care if she had breakfast at 10 or 11.30 am, you have nothing to do afterwards. -
Cooking breakfast: - For breakfast she has a coffee with milk heated in the microwave and she still keeps doing that. -
Eating breakfast: - For breakfast she has a coffee with milk heated in the microwave and she still keeps doing that. -
Watching TV: - Her hobbie was to watch TV and she keeps doing it (...) Her obsession and entertainment is the television -

Gone out waling: - At first she did not want to go anywhere. She did not want to go outside the house. Once she was taking medication for depression well, it seems shes livelier and yes, she goes out more, and on every occasion we have I take her out -
Gone out: - I try to carry her around when I go out, we go out shopping or to the market, or we go see my sisters but most of the times she is in no mood of going out -
Cooking supper: - But the meals she does not do them anymore -
